Dialogue: 0,0:00:01.23,0:00:03.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:03.22,0:00:04.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Is there something you're not telling me?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:04.65,0:00:05.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,When we're in meetings together,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:05.85,0:00:07.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,don't ever call my ideas "Ridiculous."
Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.90,0:00:09.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Come on. I'm being serious.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:09.40,0:00:10.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So am I.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.25,0:00:12.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Merrill's son asked for personal advice.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:12.13,0:00:14.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- And he picked you. - I know, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:14.06,0:00:17.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A surgeon needs to communicate. Can Dr. Murphy do that?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.12,0:00:18.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Can he do that under stress?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.20,0:00:20.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Can he do that knowing that a human life
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.73,0:00:22.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,literally hangs in the balance?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:26.73,0:00:28.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you, Dr. Kalu.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.87,0:00:30.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're welcome. It's a special blend.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.83,0:00:32.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I roast the beans myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.90,0:00:34.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Smells like leather.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.63,0:00:36.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then none for you, Murphy.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.82,0:00:38.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't drink coffee.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:40.69,0:00:41.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It is dead in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.01,0:00:44.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's why they call it the graveyard shift.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:44.13,0:00:47.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, well, I call it paradise. You my trauma virgins?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:47.02,0:00:50.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ah, Doctors Murphy, Kalu, Browne --
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.06,0:00:51.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,meet Dr. Audrey Lim,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:51.61,0:00:53.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,your attending for the evening.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.20,0:00:53.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Coffee?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.86,0:00:55.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,He roasts the beans himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.80,0:00:57.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kiss ass.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.22,0:01:01.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,E.R.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:03.31,0:01:05.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How long? Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:05.82,0:01:06.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Listen up, everybody!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.89,0:01:08.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We got a mass cas coming in.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.34,0:01:10.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's a bus crash, two dozen passengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.28,0:01:13.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Transfer all patients waiting for beds up to the nursing units.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:13.45,0:01:15.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Have maintenance bring down cots.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:15.13,0:01:17.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We're gonna convert the waiting room into triage.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:17.18,0:01:19.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No one goes home till we're all clear!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:19.11,0:01:20.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Page everyone on call. I don't care what department they are.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.77,0:01:23.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Tonight, everybody's trauma. Glove up and line up.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:32.41,0:01:34.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,EMTs will have triaged onsite,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:34.21,0:01:36.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,so the patients are gonna come in tagged.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:37.28,0:01:39.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I love these blank faces right before Armageddon.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:39.40,0:01:40.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Trauma color coding -- who knows it?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:40.96,0:01:43.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Green -- walking wounded. Yellow -- observation.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:43.03,0:01:44.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Red needs immediate attention.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:44.33,0:01:45.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And black go straight to the morgue.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:00.20,0:02:01.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All right, red tags, front of the line!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:01.65,0:02:03.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Red tags, front of the line.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:03.04,0:02:04.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wedding bus blew a tire and flipped!
Dialogue: 0,0:02:04.98,0:02:06.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,26-year-old female.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:06.40,0:02:09.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Second- and third-degree burns to her neck, chest, and left arm.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:09.23,0:02:10.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Kalu, you're up.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:12.68,0:02:13.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Trauma Six.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.56,0:02:15.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Guy was ejected 30 feet from the vehicle.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:15.39,0:02:16.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Multiple chest contusions,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:16.41,0:02:17.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,acute respiratory distress on the scene,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:17.94,0:02:19.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,sluggish pupillary response.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:19.14,0:02:20.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- How long have you been doing CPR? - 12 minutes.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:20.81,0:02:22.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Have you shocked him? - Three times.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:22.08,0:02:23.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We got to crack him. Dr. Browne, I got this.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:23.86,0:02:25.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You take the next one. All right, Bay Five.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.41,0:02:32.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We secured the foreign object and staunched the bleeding,
Dialogue: 0,0:02:32.47,0:02:34.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,but didn't want to touch it otherwise.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:38.10,0:02:40.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Good thing. It nicked her carotid. - What is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:40.03,0:02:42.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Right now it's a little Dutch boy keeping her from bleeding out.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:42.52,0:02:44.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Pulse ox is dropping. She's at 87.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:45.31,0:02:47.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,O2 sats down to 83.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:49.38,0:02:50.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Forget about the neck, Claire.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:50.64,0:02:51.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Treat her like any other patient.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.78,0:02:52.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What are the first steps?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:53.23,0:02:54.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Airway, breathing, circulation.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:54.75,0:02:56.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Good. Grab a kit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.96,0:03:21.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I need help here! Somebody, help!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.39,0:03:22.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Murphy, go!
Dialogue: 0,0:03:26.46,0:03:27.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Let's go.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:28.50,0:03:29.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Trauma Three.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:44.24,0:03:45.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I can't stop the bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:49.16,0:03:51.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- He's bleeding out. - Do something.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:58.47,0:04:01.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I need a urinary catheter, 14-gauge needle,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:01.76,0:04:03.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,arterial guide wire, occlusion balloon,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.65,0:04:06.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,and 20 cc of saline, stat.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:29.17,0:04:30.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- What's he doing? - I have no idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:30.88,0:04:33.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, you don't have one, so I'm making a REBOA.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:34.46,0:04:35.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A what?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.50,0:04:38.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A REBOA.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:39.62,0:04:40.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Is that even a word?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:40.60,0:04:44.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A REBOA will occlude the damaged artery and stop the bleeding.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.42,0:05:03.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Release the pressure.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:10.81,0:05:13.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,BP is stabilizing. 90 over 60.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.59,0:05:19.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nice work, Dr. Murphy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:19.53,0:05:20.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I made a REBOA.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:23.26,0:05:24.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oxygen is dropping to 89.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.77,0:05:25.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All right. Light.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:26.48,0:05:27.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Open wide for me.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:27.62,0:05:29.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Throat's swollen from smoke inhalation.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:29.45,0:05:30.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cric kit.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.65,0:05:33.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Do you see soot in her mouth or nose? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:33.39,0:05:35.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She doesn't need a cric. She needs an escharotomy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.96,0:05:49.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sats are going back up. 92 and rising.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:49.30,0:05:50.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Circumferential neck burns.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.73,0:05:53.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The shrinking charred skin is acting like a noose.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.54,0:05:55.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Escharotomy relieves the constriction.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.39,0:05:58.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Are you getting enough air now, ma'am?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:58.24,0:05:59.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes. Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.98,0:06:01.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Now get her out of this petri dish
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.39,0:06:03.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,and into an isolation ward in the burn unit ASAP.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:03.74,0:06:04.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:07.40,0:06:08.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Your heart's a bit muffled.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.40,0:06:10.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Am I having a heart attack?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:10.72,0:06:12.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, but it's not completely good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.61,0:06:13.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Cardiac tamponade.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:13.71,0:06:15.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,He needs a pericardiocentesis.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.01,0:06:16.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes, I'm aware of that.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:16.86,0:06:19.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,18-gauge and 55 cc syringe, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:19.88,0:06:21.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We need a FAST ultrasound in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:21.12,0:06:22.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,They're both in use.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:23.79,0:06:25.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You don't have imaging. You could puncture his heart.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:25.56,0:06:28.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Is the xiphoid in the same place as it was 20 years ago?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:47.53,0:06:48.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A REBOA.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:48.95,0:06:49.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Ballsy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:50.27,0:06:51.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Could've gone really wrong.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:51.52,0:06:53.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes, well, it didn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.82,0:06:55.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's a cowboy move --
Dialogue: 0,0:06:55.71,0:06:58.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,something you would never even dream of trying.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:59.15,0:07:00.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How many times is Shaun gonna have to prove himself
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.80,0:07:02.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,before you give him a shot?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:04.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dr. Rolendez, O.R. 6.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.24,0:07:14.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What happened in the E.R.?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:15.05,0:07:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Swan girl came in and you hesitated.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.05,0:07:19.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I wasn't hesitating. I was thinking of a game plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:19.37,0:07:21.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Murphy was thinking of the game plan.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:21.42,0:07:22.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You got overwhelmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:23.31,0:07:24.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I wasn't.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.25,0:07:26.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,First trauma, it happens.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:26.22,0:07:29.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You have to think clearly, quickly, methodically.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.51,0:07:31.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You need to think a little more like Shaun.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:33.15,0:07:35.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A little more. Not identically.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.32,0:07:54.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How you doing?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.22,0:07:55.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:56.95,0:07:58.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sorry. That's a stupid question.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.47,0:08:04.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're maxed out on morphine.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:04.03,0:08:06.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll hold off until it reloads.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:11.48,0:08:12.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How bad is it?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.68,0:08:15.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We're making good progress.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:15.44,0:08:18.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll have to... debride any deroofed blisters
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.41,0:08:19.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,to prevent a secondary nosocomial and then --
Dialogue: 0,0:08:19.85,0:08:20.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I need a mirror.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:21.60,0:08:22.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's the least you can do
Dialogue: 0,0:08:22.62,0:08:24.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,since you can't even look me in the eye.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.15,0:08:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, my God.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:52.39,0:08:56.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Do you know how many hideous $300 bridesmaid dresses
Dialogue: 0,0:08:56.74,0:08:59.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I've had to buy in the last two years?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.28,0:09:03.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I decided that when I got married,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:03.86,0:09:06.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,my bridesmaids are gonna wear black cocktail dresses
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.41,0:09:09.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,so they can use them again, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:14.22,0:09:15.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But now...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:17.16,0:09:19.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,now I-I'm Freddy Krueger.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:21.39,0:09:23.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Who's gonna want to marry this?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.08,0:09:28.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm gonna find a nurse,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.35,0:09:30.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,have her adjust your... your morphine drip.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:37.21,0:09:38.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:38.49,0:09:39.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You hit your face.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.56,0:09:41.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Your jaw got stuck. It hurts.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:41.22,0:09:43.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So, this shot I just gave you is gonna knock you out
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.21,0:09:44.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,so that I can fix that.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.30,0:09:45.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hang tight.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.82,0:09:47.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Crash patients status check? - 23 people total.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:47.83,0:09:50.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,One fatality on site, lost one in the E.R.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.02,0:09:50.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Examined all the red tags.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:50.92,0:09:53.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Got 13 yellow and green still in the waiting room.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:53.10,0:09:55.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- I'll take whoever's up next. - Marco Magallenes...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:55.55,0:09:57.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,severed femoral artery, crushed femur.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.37,0:10:00.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I did the REBOA and then installed a temporary shunt.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.50,0:10:03.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Here are his CT and MRI results.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:07.62,0:10:09.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Find someone else for whoever's up next.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:12.24,0:10:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, finally.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:31.79,0:10:33.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Excuse me. Are you Marco's family?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:33.71,0:10:34.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:35.38,0:10:38.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We just found out that my cousin didn't survive the accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:38.71,0:10:39.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:41.85,0:10:43.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- It's a bit much. - I'm so sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:43.68,0:10:46.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm Dr. Melendez, and this is Dr. Murphy.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:46.81,0:10:48.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm Ricardo.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:48.39,0:10:50.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm M-Marco's father.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.02,0:10:53.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This is, uh, his mother, Lorena, and this is Sonia.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.36,0:10:55.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,They were getting married tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:56.35,0:10:57.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How's my son?
Dialogue: 0,0:10:57.39,0:10:59.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Marco's femur was completely shattered,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:59.34,0:11:01.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,and his lower leg isn't getting enough blood.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:03.03,0:11:04.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Can you save his leg?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:04.78,0:11:07.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Marco suffered too much bone fragmentation.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:07.45,0:11:08.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We can't fix it.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:09.73,0:11:11.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Our only choice is to amputate.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:13.95,0:11:15.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mija.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:28.63,0:11:30.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Bay Five needs a grade three hyphema.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:30.94,0:11:32.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Head CT and page ophthalmology?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:32.43,0:11:33.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You read my mind.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:33.82,0:11:34.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Been a while.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:34.50,0:11:36.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How you holding up pulling an all-nighter?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:37.23,0:11:39.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll manage, but if you can find me a caffeine IV,
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.33,0:11:40.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Please move! - it'd be helpful.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.26,0:11:44.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Tough night. - Yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:44.88,0:11:45.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thanks for coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:46.07,0:11:47.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's part of the job.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.80,0:11:50.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So, when's the big day?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.46,0:11:52.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We haven't set it yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.14,0:11:54.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Oh, where is it gonna be?
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.13,0:11:56.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We'll figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.02,0:11:58.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Maybe a beach somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.65,0:11:59.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We should talk about this later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:00.10,0:12:01.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What? I like beaches.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:01.71,0:12:03.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you have a more romantic idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.35,0:12:06.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My family likes churches.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.53,0:12:10.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We should talk about this later.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:10.96,0:12:14.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dr. Lim, I think one of your yellows is about to turn red.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:16.69,0:12:18.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I've got my wedding all planned out.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:18.77,0:12:21.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I've got the dress, and I've got the flowers.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.08,0:12:22.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All I need is a groom.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:24.45,0:12:25.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You available, Dr. Murphy?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.55,0:12:27.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:27.94,0:12:29.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You don't want some love?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:30.01,0:12:33.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No. No, I don't. I don't want love.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.35,0:12:39.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dr. Glassman, neural consult, bay three.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:40.01,0:12:40.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.74,0:12:47.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I was here first.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:48.29,0:12:49.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Shaun.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.24,0:12:51.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Shaun!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.53,0:12:53.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My patient's scans are very important.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:53.40,0:12:54.85,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, my patient's important, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.85,0:12:57.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I need to see my patient's scans.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:58.24,0:12:59.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Is your patient pre-op or post-op?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.62,0:13:00.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Pre-op.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:02.17,0:13:03.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay, I'll give you the computer,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:03.71,0:13:05.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,but you need to apologize first.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:05.08,0:13:07.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay, I'm sorry. Turn it on.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:12.75,0:13:15.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why was Marco's family crying when Dr. Melendez
Dialogue: 0,0:13:15.86,0:13:18.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,told them his leg would need to be amputated?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:19.70,0:13:23.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, their son's leg is about to be cut off.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:23.03,0:13:25.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's sad. Crying is normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.58,0:13:28.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But when your options are amputation or death,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.24,0:13:29.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,amputation is good news.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:29.95,0:13:32.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,People need time to adjust to big changes.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:33.19,0:13:36.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Marco's family didn't even get a chance to pray for a miracle.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.40,0:13:46.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,}It's not possible.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.60,0:13:50.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The bone damage is too severe.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.68,0:13:53.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A rod implantation won't work.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.42,0:13:55.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,There's nothing to anchor into,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.97,0:13:59.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,and the shunt won't last long enough to do reconstruction.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.05,0:14:02.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,There are no other options.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:06.36,0:14:08.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What if we could replace the entire femur?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:12.66,0:14:14.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We're making him a new femur.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:14.33,0:14:15.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,With a 3D printer?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.22,0:14:20.02,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,3D-printed bones have only successfully been done with the mandible.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:20.02,0:14:20.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.20,0:14:23.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- That's a fairly small bone. - We know.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.07,0:14:25.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,A femur has to support the weight of the entire body.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.19,0:14:27.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This one will be titanium. It can work.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.67,0:14:29.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's an interesting idea...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.57,0:14:31.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,but I need to think on it.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:32.29,0:14:34.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Right now we still got seven yellow tags waiting.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.98,0:14:36.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What do you have to think about?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:36.15,0:14:37.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- It's a good idea. - It's a brilliant idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.92,0:14:39.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The kid has brilliant ideas. That doesn't mean --
Dialogue: 0,0:14:39.28,0:14:40.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, it was my idea,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:40.61,0:14:41.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,and I'm aware of the risks --
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.81,0:14:43.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,infection, clotting, hardware failure...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:43.88,0:14:44.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Death.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.87,0:14:47.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- It wasn't your idea. - It was my idea!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.11,0:14:48.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And the risks are significant,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:48.56,0:14:49.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,but isn't that their call?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.87,0:14:51.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Don't we have to... - Maybe he said something,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.82,0:14:53.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,and then you said something, and together, you --
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.17,0:14:55.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My idea. Completely my idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.12,0:14:58.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The "brilliant" idea is 100% my brilliant idea.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.10,0:14:59.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why is that a problem for you?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.58,0:15:01.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Maybe because I've known you for six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.52,0:15:04.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Every day we learn new things.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.72,0:15:06.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Today, you learned I'm brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:07.09,0:15:08.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The idea was brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.26,0:15:09.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And it was mine.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:10.03,0:15:11.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And if anyone can do this brilliant surgery,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.89,0:15:12.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,it's you.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:14.07,0:15:15.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Flattery --
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.40,0:15:17.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,also brilliant.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:25.11,0:15:26.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Sleeping on the job?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.50,0:15:28.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Just needed some fresh air.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.03,0:15:32.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Feels like I'm suffocating in there.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:34.43,0:15:36.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She's in pain, spilling her guts out,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:36.41,0:15:37.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,and every time I open my mouth,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.73,0:15:38.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I sound like an idiot.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:39.98,0:15:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dr. Kalu -- unable to talk to women.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:42.62,0:15:43.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,There's a first.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:43.76,0:15:45.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If you're not gonna be helpful, Claire, just leave.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:48.41,0:15:51.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You don't need to talk. Just listen to her.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:52.85,0:15:55.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You get to come out here, clear your head.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:55.65,0:15:56.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She's trapped in there,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:56.72,0:15:58.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,alone with her thoughts, her fears.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:58.73,0:16:00.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You don't think she wants to get out?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.70,0:16:03.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You are her escape.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:11.06,0:16:13.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You want to put a fake femur into Marco's leg?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:13.67,0:16:15.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's not fake. It's real.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:15.61,0:16:18.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's not a real bone. We're making it out of titanium.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:18.17,0:16:19.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's still real.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.10,0:16:20.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's incredible.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:20.72,0:16:23.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And Marco will be able to walk, run, climb?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.24,0:16:24.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And swim.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:25.39,0:16:27.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hopefully. That's the intention.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:27.75,0:16:30.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, have you done the surgery before?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:30.08,0:16:31.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- I haven't. - We'll be the first.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:34.21,0:16:35.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, nobody has ever attempted this surgery
Dialogue: 0,0:16:35.78,0:16:37.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,with a bone as large as the femur.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:37.80,0:16:40.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I believe it's a viable option, but there are risks.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:40.52,0:16:43.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Risks? Could Marco die?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:43.01,0:16:45.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,In my estimation, there's a 10% chance he won't make it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.92,0:16:46.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Then no.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:47.14,0:16:48.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm not losing my son.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:48.39,0:16:51.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Wait. If there's a chance we can save Marco's leg,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:51.25,0:16:52.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,we should at least discuss this some more.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:52.71,0:16:53.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's what he'd want.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.88,0:16:55.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,He'd want to live.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:55.39,0:16:56.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,He'd want to have a life.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:57.52,0:16:58.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I know him.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:59.03,0:17:00.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,He'd want to take the chance.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:00.66,0:17:02.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I will never forgive myself if Marco died
Dialogue: 0,0:17:02.98,0:17:04.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,because I made a reckless decision.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.38,0:17:07.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Whose decision is this?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:07.99,0:17:09.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Does he have a healthcare proxy?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:09.78,0:17:11.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't know what that is.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:11.58,0:17:13.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,When the accident happened,
Dialogue: 0,0:17:13.18,0:17:15.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,were you on the way to your wedding or on the way back?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:15.08,0:17:16.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We were headed to the wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:18.01,0:17:19.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Marco's parents are the next of kin.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:19.94,0:17:20.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,They decide.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.43,0:17:28.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Please...
Dialogue: 0,0:17:29.53,0:17:31.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,amputate our son's leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:35.98,0:17:36.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Murphy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:44.14,0:17:47.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why is the primary closure on the stump so vital in amputation surgery?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:47.78,0:17:49.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,For a proper prosthetic fitting.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:50.25,0:17:51.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why are you marrying Jessica?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:53.92,0:17:55.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why does anyone get married?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:56.31,0:17:57.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:59.55,0:18:00.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I love her.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:01.40,0:18:03.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't understand why having someone to love
Dialogue: 0,0:18:03.80,0:18:05.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,is so important to everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:07.53,0:18:08.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You have to stand down.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:09.21,0:18:11.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- You can't amputate Marco's leg. - Why not?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:11.35,0:18:14.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I filed an emergency injunction to stop the surgery.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:18.41,0:18:19.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You were in a car accident.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:20.04,0:18:21.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Your neck was punctured.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.87,0:18:23.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,The repair surgery went well.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:23.34,0:18:24.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're gonna have to stay put for a week
Dialogue: 0,0:18:24.72,0:18:26.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,before we can release you.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:27.61,0:18:29.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're very lucky to be alive.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:37.26,0:18:41.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,My wife, Jenna Hensel -- is she okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:41.83,0:18:43.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Can I see her?
Dialogue: 0,0:18:48.09,0:18:49.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She's not listed.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.95,0:18:51.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That's a good thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:51.46,0:18:53.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She's probably still in the waiting room.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:53.68,0:18:55.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'll find her and bring her up.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:55.42,0:18:57.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She'll be relieved to know you're okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:58.25,0:18:59.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.41,0:19:02.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,What the hell am I supposed to do with an unconscious patient
Dialogue: 0,0:19:02.70,0:19:03.91,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,whose leg is a ticking time bomb?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:03.92,0:19:05.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Judge Singh is en route.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:05.16,0:19:08.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She wants to hear from both parties and the doctors on the case.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:08.03,0:19:09.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I have to testify?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:09.78,0:19:10.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Hopefully not. - Hopefully not.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:10.77,0:19:12.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I thought you would be happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:12.81,0:19:14.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You thought you could save the leg,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:14.15,0:19:16.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,and I didn't want that not happening because the parents
Dialogue: 0,0:19:16.22,0:19:17.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,are afraid to make a tough call.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:17.41,0:19:18.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's their call to make.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:18.82,0:19:20.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And if the accident happened an hour later,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:20.53,0:19:22.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,it would be the wife's.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.28,0:19:23.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And she wants the fake leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:23.48,0:19:24.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's not fake.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.69,0:19:28.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I thought you didn't believe in just blindly following protocol.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:28.89,0:19:30.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,He's their son.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:30.10,0:19:31.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Nobody's gonna love him more than them.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.69,0:19:32.69,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Seriously?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:32.69,0:19:35.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,All parents love all children more than anybody else?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:35.90,0:19:37.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,People get divorced all the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:38.07,0:19:39.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How often do they give up their kids?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:39.25,0:19:40.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,So, if this was us,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:40.83,0:19:42.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,you'd want your parents to decide over me?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.46,0:19:44.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- I didn't say that. - You kind of did.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:45.87,0:19:48.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I was saying, there needs to be rules,
Dialogue: 0,0:19:48.56,0:19:50.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,that there needs to be bright red lines telling us
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.74,0:19:52.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,who gets to make these calls.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:52.75,0:19:54.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's the parents' call.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:54.16,0:19:55.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:55.85,0:19:56.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Now it's the judge's.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:57.78,0:19:59.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How much time does Marco have left on the temporary shunt?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:59.76,0:20:01.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Three hours,
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.10,0:20:03.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,and then his leg will die.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:06.65,0:20:07.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:16.97,0:20:18.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Dr. Torture returns.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:19.60,0:20:21.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Thought I'd scared you off for good.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:22.17,0:20:23.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Pick a movie.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:24.14,0:20:26.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You deserve to get out of this room for a little while, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.28,0:20:31.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You think "Groundhog Day" is gonna make a difference?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:32.58,0:20:35.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,"I'm torturing you, but, hey, you get to watch a funny movie."
Dialogue: 0,0:20:36.54,0:20:38.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,That is sort of what I was going for, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:42.91,0:20:43.78,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I'm sorry.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:47.01,0:20:48.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I wish there was something else I could do.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:49.82,0:20:51.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,How do you know there isn't?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:51.01,0:20:52.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This is protocol. This is what they teach us.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:52.64,0:20:53.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I lucked out.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:54.33,0:20:57.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I got the world's greatest expert on burn victims?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.11,0:20:59.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You know everything that can be done.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:03.97,0:21:07.31,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,He loves to rock-climb, scuba dive, bungee-jump.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:07.31,0:21:08.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,This is insane.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:09.09,0:21:12.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,His leg is literally dying while we sit here reminiscing.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.42,0:21:15.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Please. We're trying to figure out what your son would want.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:15.54,0:21:17.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- He would want to live. - I want that, too,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:17.30,0:21:20.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,but if there's a way that we can save Marco's leg,
Dialogue: 0,0:21:21.01,0:21:22.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,he'd want me to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:22.38,0:21:26.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mija, Do you know what he wanted most of all?
Dialogue: 0,0:21:29.09,0:21:30.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,He wanted to marry you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:31.05,0:21:34.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,He wanted to spend his life with you, have children with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:34.14,0:21:36.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Now, he can do all that.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:36.24,0:21:39.87,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,He can be happy with a prosthetic leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:41.39,0:21:43.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,He's young, and he's strong.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:44.06,0:21:45.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mija, he can get through this.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:51.81,0:21:54.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- When we met -- - I don't care about your stories.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:55.09,0:21:58.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't care that you met rock-climbing
Dialogue: 0,0:21:58.88,0:22:00.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,or kayaking or whatever.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:01.02,0:22:03.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- I just want -- - We met in rehab.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:14.14,0:22:15.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Hey, are either of you Jenna Hensel?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.76,0:22:19.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I haven't seen Jenna since we took pictures at the hotel.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:19.36,0:22:20.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,But she got on the bus?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:20.84,0:22:22.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Yeah, she was sitting with Noomi.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.40,0:22:30.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I think she's still out there.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:31.10,0:22:33.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- Hey, guys! We've got to go back. - Where?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:33.04,0:22:34.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,To the crash site. Now.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:35.89,0:22:37.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,He never wanted you to know.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:40.22,0:22:41.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,He's an addict.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:41.82,0:22:45.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,He replaced one addiction for another one -- a healthier one.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:45.17,0:22:48.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- But he needs -- - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:48.51,0:22:51.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,He needs to wakeboard or he'll drink himself to death?
Dialogue: 0,0:22:52.16,0:22:54.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,- This is ridiculous. - No, it's not!
Dialogue: 0,0:22:54.42,0:22:56.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,We talked about it a lot.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:56.27,0:22:58.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It's pretty much all you do in rehab.
Dialogue: 0,0:22:58.47,0:23:01.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Marco has clarity for the first time in his life.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:02.05,0:23:03.66,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,He knows what makes him happy.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:03.66,0:23:05.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,He knows his weaknesses.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.26,0:23:08.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,He's not as strong as you think.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:09.62,0:23:11.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And that's okay, but --
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.10,0:23:13.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Marco cheated on you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.01,0:23:18.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It was about a month ago.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:18.98,0:23:21.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,He was overwhelmed with the wedding and the planning.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:22.59,0:23:24.48,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,He ran into an ex-girlfriend.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:24.48,0:23:26.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It only happened once.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:28.15,0:23:29.41,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:30.57,0:23:33.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You're upset that he had secrets from you, so --
Dialogue: 0,0:23:33.72,0:23:35.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, she's not lying.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.60,0:23:40.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Mija, he -- he was -- he was so upset.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:40.72,0:23:41.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,He does love you.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:41.71,0:23:44.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay, maybe we're digressing here a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.30,0:23:45.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,And we really don't have the time.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:45.68,0:23:46.95,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,It matters.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.83,0:23:50.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,She doesn't know him like --
Dialogue: 0,0:23:52.29,0:23:54.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,maybe none of us do, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.56,0:24:00.28,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,but we are his parents, and you're not his wife. Yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:16.67,0:24:18.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay. Get the cops. Check everywhere --
Dialogue: 0,0:24:18.24,0:24:20.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,other side of the road, bushes, trees.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:20.22,0:24:21.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,If she was ejected from the bus,
Dialogue: 0,0:24:21.11,0:24:23.07,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,she could be 40, 50 feet in any direction.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:28.00,0:24:29.14,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,珍娜\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jenna!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:32.25,0:24:33.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我找到她了  我需要幫助\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I found her! I need some help!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:41.47,0:24:42.54,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她腦出血了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Okay, she's got a brain bleed.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:42.54,0:24:44.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們需要立刻帶她離開這里\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We need to get her out of here now!
Dialogue: 0,0:24:48.24,0:24:49.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,安德魯斯醫生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dr. Andrews.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:49.86,0:24:51.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我認為塞拉斯可以勝任\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I think Celez may be eligible
Dialogue: 0,0:24:51.08,0:24:52.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,實驗性骨治療\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}for an experimental bone treatment.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:53.16,0:24:54.11,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說說看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Sell it to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:54.16,0:24:55.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我做了一些研究\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, I've been doing some digging.
Dialogue: 0,0:24:55.63,0:24:57.70,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,圣地亞哥社區醫院的燒傷科\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}San Diego Community Hospital's burn unit
Dialogue: 0,0:24:57.70,0:24:59.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在遵循一家巴西醫院的協議\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}has been following a Brazilian hospital's protocol
Dialogue: 0,0:24:59.80,0:25:01.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,用羅非魚魚皮包裹燒傷部位\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}to wrap burns in tilapia skins.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:01.45,0:25:04.22,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道使用魚皮聽起來有點瘋狂\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now -- Now, I know fish skins sound a bit crazy,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:04.22,0:25:07.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我覺得我們在這里也可以做\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}but -- but I was thinking we could do the same thing here.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:07.72,0:25:10.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,卡盧醫生  你的想法很棒\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dr. Kalu, I applaud your thinking.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:10.20,0:25:12.94,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-但我們  -羅非魚皮所含膠原蛋白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- But we -- - Tilapia skins contain more collagen proteins --
Dialogue: 0,0:25:12.94,0:25:15.25,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,比人類皮膚還多  一號三號都有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}both types 1 and 3 -- than even human skin,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:15.26,0:25:16.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有助于修復組織\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}which aids in tissue repair,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:16.54,0:25:18.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-就不需要移植皮膚了  -卡盧醫生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- negating the need for grafts. - Dr. Kalu.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:18.04,0:25:19.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-并能加速皮膚恢復  減少  -卡盧醫生\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- It's shown to accelerate healing, would reduce... - Dr. Kalu.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:19.43,0:25:21.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,避免感染的風險并降低了病人切割皮膚之痛\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the risk of infection and cut down on the patient's physical pain.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:22.40,0:25:24.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你說完了嗎  還是說你想再打斷我\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you finished, or would you like to cut me off again?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:25.47,0:25:27.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們這樣來  可以嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Okay, let's follow this through, shall we?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:27.98,0:25:30.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得提出一個實驗性治療的可行建議\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You have to come up with a proposal for the experimental treatment,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:30.57,0:25:32.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,機構審查委員會通過之后\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}get it approved by our institutional review board,
Dialogue: 0,0:25:32.83,0:25:36.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你去提取醫學級別的羅非魚魚皮  然后再...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}get your hands on medical-grade tilapia skins, and then we...
Dialogue: 0,0:25:36.38,0:25:38.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許你可以幫助我加快進程\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, I thought you could help expedite the process.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:40.98,0:25:43.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你認為我可以幫你從三個月減到兩小時\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You think I could bring it down from three months to two hours?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:45.43,0:25:46.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你做完清創術了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You finish the debridement?
Dialogue: 0,0:25:47.64,0:25:50.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-之后就交給我吧  -好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Okay, I'll take over from here. - Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:51.45,0:25:53.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,掙脫思維定勢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Keep thinking outside the box.
Dialogue: 0,0:25:53.42,0:25:54.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有主動性是好事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Initiative is good.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:04.83,0:26:06.40,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我來了  給她使用呼吸氣囊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm in. Bag her.
Dialogue: 0,0:26:06.41,0:26:07.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你拿來電鉆了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Did you get me the drill?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:07.49,0:26:08.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,消防車上有  怎么回事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The fire truck had one. What's going on?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:08.97,0:26:09.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的瞳孔擴張\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Her pupil's blown.
