Dialogue: 0,0:32:17.78,0:32:19.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,心電圖正常\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}EKG is normal.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:21.53,0:32:26.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,金  我要聽到類似「變化」和「增量」的詞\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Okay. Kim, I want to hear words like "Variability" and "Delta".
Dialogue: 0,0:32:26.17,0:32:27.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,說給我聽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Give them to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:29.50,0:32:31.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在耐心等待\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm waiting patiently.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:32.75,0:32:34.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么也沒有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm not getting anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:35.31,0:32:36.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給我看看\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Show me.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:44.48,0:32:45.49,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,檢查引線\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Check the leads.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:52.78,0:32:53.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是沒有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Still nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:54.56,0:32:56.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也許是神經重塑\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Maybe there will be some neuroplasticity.
Dialogue: 0,0:32:57.02,0:33:00.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的大腦自己重新連接\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Her brain -- I-it could rewire itself.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:00.77,0:33:01.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}No.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:04.06,0:33:05.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,沒有腦部活動\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Zero brain activity.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:05.89,0:33:07.65,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不知道為什么  但她去世了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't know why, but she's gone.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:26.63,0:33:27.37,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:27.52,0:33:29.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的神經外科病人今晚死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your neurosurgery patient that died tonight --
Dialogue: 0,0:33:29.68,0:33:31.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有件事你該知道\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}there's something you should know.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:31.64,0:33:32.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:40.55,0:33:42.63,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,馬爾科  我要你嘗試動動你的腳趾\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Now, Marco, I want you to try and move your toes.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:54.33,0:33:55.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I can't.
Dialogue: 0,0:33:55.70,0:33:56.55,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他還好嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is he okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:56.55,0:33:57.52,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們不確定骨...\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're not sure if the bone --
Dialogue: 0,0:33:57.52,0:33:58.42,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不會死吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He's not gonna die?
Dialogue: 0,0:33:58.42,0:34:00.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他不會被感染吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}H-He's not gonna get an infection?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.13,0:34:00.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-他的身體不會排斥... -不\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- His body's not gonna reject -- - No, no.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:00.93,0:34:02.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們密切監控他\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We're monitoring him very closely.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:02.81,0:34:04.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-最大的威脅... -他動了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- The biggest threat is behind -- - He moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:05.52,0:34:06.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他動了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}He moved.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:13.74,0:34:14.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,成功了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It worked.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:16.30,0:34:17.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有漫長的復原期等著你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You'll have a long recovery ahead --
Dialogue: 0,0:34:17.82,0:34:19.57,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,好幾個月的物理治療\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}months of physical therapy.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:19.87,0:34:21.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不過現在  你應該好好休息\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But for now, all you have to do is rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:21.29,0:34:22.30,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:23.00,0:34:26.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝你救了我的命  挽救了我的腿\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thank you for saving my life -- for saving my leg.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:27.79,0:34:29.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-謝謝  -不用謝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Thank you. - You're welcome, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:34.61,0:34:36.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,準備好接著辦完我們的事了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Are you ready to finish what we started?
Dialogue: 0,0:34:38.77,0:34:40.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,先好起來再說\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Get well first.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:41.59,0:34:43.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,有的是時間辦婚禮\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}There's plenty of time for a wedding.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:52.05,0:34:53.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-謝謝  -不用謝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- Thank you. - You're welcome, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:34:53.89,0:34:54.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:02.73,0:35:03.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你看起來很好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You look good.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:03.82,0:35:06.06,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,堅強  就像潛水俠\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Tough. Like Aquaman.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:10.62,0:35:12.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我看起來像壽司\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I look like sushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:12.37,0:35:14.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,大家都愛吃壽司\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Everybody loves sushi.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:15.77,0:35:17.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,只需要六個月\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It's only for six months.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:17.05,0:35:19.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你的新皮膚應該就能完全長好了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Your new skin should have completely grown in by then.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:19.37,0:35:20.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,瘢痕應該會很小\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Should have minor scarring.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:22.17,0:35:23.39,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,謝謝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Thank you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:25.81,0:35:27.12,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我誤會你了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I misjudged you.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:29.42,0:35:30.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你對我的評判很準確\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You judged me just right.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:43.36,0:35:44.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她還在睡嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Is she still sleeping?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:45.87,0:35:47.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,-你還沒告訴她嗎  -沒有\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}- You haven't told her yet? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:35:49.48,0:35:51.00,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,能出來一下嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Can I have a moment please?
Dialogue: 0,0:35:51.96,0:35:52.81,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,當然\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Of course.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:00.22,0:36:03.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你在事故現場發現珍娜后多久\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}How soon after you found Jenna at the crash site
Dialogue: 0,0:36:03.53,0:36:04.93,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給她插的管\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}did you intubate her?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:04.99,0:36:06.29,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,幾乎是立刻就插了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Almost immediately.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:07.07,0:36:08.47,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我按壓她的胸骨\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I did a sternal rub.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:08.69,0:36:10.21,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她表現出去大腦強直\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She had decerebrate posturing.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:10.21,0:36:11.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的左側瞳孔已經散大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Her left pupil was blown.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:11.97,0:36:13.53,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道她出現了硬膜下血腫\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I knew she had a subdural hematoma,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:13.53,0:36:16.19,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,所以我插了管  鉆了孔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}so I intubated, did the burr hole.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:16.63,0:36:18.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并且她還有連枷胸\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She also had a flail chest.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:19.43,0:36:21.82,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你插管之后檢查她的呼吸了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Did you check her breathing after you intubated her?
Dialogue: 0,0:36:21.82,0:36:22.56,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,查了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:25.04,0:36:27.90,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我覺得我應該查了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Well, at least I-I think I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:30.07,0:36:34.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,利姆醫生說珍娜到急診的時候\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Dr. Lim told me that when Jenna came into the E.R.,
Dialogue: 0,0:36:34.11,0:36:36.04,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她的呼吸并不正常\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}she wasn't ventilating properly.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:36.04,0:36:37.98,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你插管插得太深了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You inserted the tube too deep
Dialogue: 0,0:36:38.22,0:36:40.75,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,插進了她傷側肺的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}into her right main stem bronchus
Dialogue: 0,0:36:41.00,0:36:42.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,右主支氣管\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}of her injured lung.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:43.21,0:36:44.79,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們沒法估計\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}We had no way of knowing
Dialogue: 0,0:36:45.29,0:36:49.18,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,在給她做腦電圖前她已經缺氧了多久\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}how long she was hypoxic before we gave her the EEG.
Dialogue: 0,0:36:59.70,0:37:03.72,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我在她顱骨上鉆了一個非常完美的孔\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I drilled a perfect burr hole into her skull
Dialogue: 0,0:37:03.72,0:37:05.10,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,還是在夜里  在馬路邊\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}on the side of the road in the middle of the night,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:05.10,0:37:07.92,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但我  我插管卻插壞了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}and I-I-I screw up her intubation?
Dialogue: 0,0:37:08.64,0:37:09.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,是的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:09.18,0:37:11.43,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,即使是高年資醫生  當時的情況\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}It was tough conditions for anyone --
Dialogue: 0,0:37:11.43,0:37:12.64,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,也是非常棘手的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}resident or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:12.81,0:37:15.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們任何人都有可能犯同樣的錯誤\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Any one of us could have made the same mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:30.17,0:37:33.05,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我曾經在急診室接診過一個女病人\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I had a woman come into the E.R. once...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:34.38,0:37:36.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,51歲  是個母親\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}a mother, 51 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:37.82,0:37:39.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,弗朗辛·帕克\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Francine Parker.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:40.36,0:37:41.71,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她有兩個兒子\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She had two boys.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:42.59,0:37:44.17,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她因為咳嗽來的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She had a cough --
Dialogue: 0,0:37:45.05,0:37:47.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,很劇烈  但也不過是個咳嗽\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}a bad one -- but a cough.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.07,0:37:49.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我給她做了檢查\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I checked her out,
Dialogue: 0,0:37:49.80,0:37:51.67,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,給她開了點抗生素就讓她回去了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}gave her some antibiotics, sent her home.
Dialogue: 0,0:37:51.87,0:37:54.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,六小時后  她被人送來急診\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Six hours later, she was rolled into the E.R..
Dialogue: 0,0:37:55.79,0:37:58.38,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她得了心臟病  我沒發現  結果\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She had had a heart attack, and I missed it, and...
Dialogue: 0,0:37:59.79,0:38:00.88,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她死了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}she died.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:04.20,0:38:06.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,從那時起\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Not one day...
Dialogue: 0,0:38:06.92,0:38:09.34,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,之后我的每一天我都會想起她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}goes by when I don't think about her.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:11.68,0:38:13.20,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,她是你的第一例\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}She was your first.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:14.94,0:38:17.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,其實  是第四例\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My fourth, actually.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:19.80,0:38:22.03,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不會忘記這種病例的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're not gonna forget this.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:22.81,0:38:24.32,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,永遠忘不了\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You never forget.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:25.20,0:38:27.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,但可能  下次遇到這些病例\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}But I don't know, maybe we're better off for it
Dialogue: 0,0:38:27.77,0:38:29.13,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我們可以做得更好\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}the next time around.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:30.80,0:38:32.83,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你得努力振作起來\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You got to find a way to keep going.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:38.51,0:38:39.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,回家去  去睡吧\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Go home. Get some rest.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:41.37,0:38:42.62,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我都還沒有告訴她\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I haven't even told her yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:42.62,0:38:43.99,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你不準去\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You're not going to.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:45.62,0:38:48.09,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你犯了個錯誤  你與此事關系太大\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}You made a mistake. You're too close to this.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:48.09,0:38:50.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我不能讓你去和家屬\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I'm not gonna allow you to talk to the family
Dialogue: 0,0:38:50.33,0:38:54.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,或院外的任何人談論這事\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}or anyone else outside this hospital about this.
Dialogue: 0,0:38:56.04,0:38:57.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,你聽明白了嗎\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Do we understand each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:38:58.92,0:38:59.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,明白\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, sir.
