Dialogue: 0,0:39:12.31,0:39:16.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(300,300)\i1}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b0\bord1\shad0\3c&HEBAF00&}♪ I'm still healing from my mistakes ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:39:18.64,0:39:22.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(300,300)\i1}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b0\bord1\shad0\3c&HEBAF00&}♪ I'll take the weight if it makes you stronger ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:39:25.25,0:39:29.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(300,300)\i1}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b0\bord1\shad0\3c&HEBAF00&}♪ I don't want to leave you in this place ♪
Dialogue: 0,0:39:34.48,0:39:36.50,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我給圣地亞哥社區醫院打電話謝謝他們\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I called San Diego Community Hospital and thanked them
Dialogue: 0,0:39:36.50,0:39:37.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,把我們納入他們的研究\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}for including us in their study.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:37.73,0:39:39.45,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,他們說他們非常樂意接納我們\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}They said they were happy to do it.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:40.39,0:39:43.76,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,并請我轉達對你的感謝\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}And they asked that I pass along their thanks to you
Dialogue: 0,0:39:43.76,0:39:47.61,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,感謝你對他們燒傷科無比慷慨的捐款\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}for your very generous donation to their burn unit.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:52.39,0:39:53.86,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我知道你家里非常有錢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I know you come from a wealthy family.
Dialogue: 0,0:39:53.86,0:39:55.77,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我也不是嫉妒  但你\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}I don't begrudge that, but you...
Dialogue: 0,0:39:56.45,0:40:00.01,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,不能每次病人有需要你就自己掏錢\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}can't open your wallet every time a patient's in need.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:01.27,0:40:04.58,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,醫患之間的關系很快就會變味的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}The lines can get real blurry real fast.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:07.01,0:40:07.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,遵命\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Yes, sir.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:31.01,0:40:35.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,{\an9\fad(300,300)\i1}{\fn方正黑体_GBK\fs18\b0\bord1\shad0\3c&HEBAF00&}♪ Who am I to try and save you? ♪
