Dialogue: 0,0:40:41.35,0:40:42.16,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,這是什么\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}What's this?
Dialogue: 0,0:40:42.95,0:40:44.35,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,我的醫學委托人文件\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}My healthcare proxy.
Dialogue: 0,0:40:44.77,0:40:46.51,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,杰西  不會有事的\N{\fn微软雅黑}{\b0}{\fs14}{\3c&H202020&}{\shad1}Jess, nothing's gonna happen.
