Dialogue: 0,0:41:10.78,0:41:12.97,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, that was quite a night.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:14.06,0:41:15.80,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Been a doctor for a long while --
Dialogue: 0,0:41:15.80,0:41:19.26,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,don't remember a night quite like that one.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:20.08,0:41:23.23,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Why did Nurse Farrar ask if I wanted love?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:23.24,0:41:24.73,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,'Cause she's a nosy...
Dialogue: 0,0:41:28.27,0:41:30.33,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Shaun, you really don't want love?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:30.89,0:41:33.44,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I loved Steve and my rabbit.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:34.40,0:41:35.46,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Not anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:36.24,0:41:37.60,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You don't love them anymore?
Dialogue: 0,0:41:38.74,0:41:40.96,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,No, I don't. They're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:41.58,0:41:43.59,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You can't love someone if they're dead.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:45.50,0:41:48.24,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Well, I've lost people I love.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:48.85,0:41:51.68,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I miss them, and it hurts, but I still love them.
Dialogue: 0,0:41:57.94,0:41:59.27,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I don't want love.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:04.38,0:42:05.15,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:09.30,0:42:10.36,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You want breakfast?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:12.99,0:42:15.74,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Can I have four pancakes instead of three?
Dialogue: 0,0:42:15.76,0:42:16.84,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,You can have five.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:17.34,0:42:18.89,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,I only want four.
Dialogue: 0,0:42:19.24,0:42:20.08,*Default,NTP,0,0,0,,Okay.
